PART 2: Clustering and cell calling¶

scVI to regress out technical artifacts

In [6]:
obj = adata.copy()
sc.pp.highly_variable_genes(obj, n_top_genes = 2000, subset = True, layer = 'counts', flavor = 'seurat_v3')
In [7]:
scvi.model.SCVI.setup_anndata(obj, layer='counts', batch_key='set')
model = scvi.model.SCVI(obj)
model.train()
